data.text:
The Rosie dress is our vision of what Marie Antoinette would wear in the countryside. The Rosie dress features princess seams on the bodice along with silk ribbon and cotton lace trims. Adjustable lace up corset detail lets you be sexy, demure, or a little bit of both. The Rosie dress is modeled here by Belle in the color Angel Blue ♡

Side zipper on wearer’s left, along with side ties and adjustable straps. Fully lined. Made with love in the USA. Self: 100% Cotton. Lining: 100% Cotton. Ribbon: 100% Silk.

♡ All dresses are made to order for sustainability. Please allow up to 6 to 8 weeks for delivery. Tayma will personally send updates as your dress is being made and shipped ♡
